data.description: Welcome to this expansive 5-acre parcel of land, recently cleared and brimming with possibilities! Located in the highly sought-after Chapel Hill Independent School District, this property offers an exceptional opportunity for those seeking to build their dream home, invest in real estate, or develop a thriving project. Boasting a substantial amount of road frontage, this property offers easy access and visibility, making it ideal for residential development.  Save time and effort with the convenience of utility services already available on the property. This invaluable feature makes it ready for immediate use or development  5 acres right off Hwy 31 heading towards Kilgore.  The acreage has been cleaned and ready for a New Mobile Home or A New Build House. NO RESTRICTIONS.    Call your realtor asap.
